channel.title: Class, Interface, or Enum expected
channel.description:
Okay, so i've been working on this server, and it's really good, but i've fixed most of the errors >.> pain in the ass.
Then there's this one error, Class, Interface, or Enum expected. This is a pain in the ass. A enum represents a bracket usually, so i've been going back in my recent code and I haven't found it. So, someone please help?
[code] src\server\model\players\packets\Commands.java:1447: error: class, interface, or enum expected public void DonatorCommands(Client c, String playerCommand) { ^ 1 error Press any key to continue . . . [/code]
If you want the file to check it, it's here: [url=http://pastebin.com/kVM8d8VM]http://pastebin.com/kVM8d8VM[/url]
